    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped spinach</strong> and<strong> halved tomatoes</strong> to the orzo with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>torn</strong> <strong>basil</strong> (save the rest for later!) and cook for a further 2-4 min or until the spinach has wilted</p><p>Once wilted, give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spinach & tomato orzo</strong></p>",
